 services. In addition, the company offers InterReach spectrum advanced multi-band in-building distributed antenna system, InterReach fusion multi-band in-building distributed antenna system, InterReach unison single-band in-building distributed antenna system, FlexWave prism das/compact radio head, and ClearGain cell site amplifiers tower and ground-mounted amplifiers. Further, it is involved in manufacturing and trading of telecom and IT-networking products. The company was incorporated in 1988 and is headquartered in Bengaluru, India. ADC India Communications Limited is a subsidiary of CommScope Connectivity LLC."}}